flowRoot.flowPara: Spoonie Living publishes daily articles that provide specific, actionable resources for all forms of chronic illness and disability, including mental illness, learning disabilities, and addiction.
Pricing: $75-100 for full article/review; $25 for brief post; $15 for social media mention. Advertisements & sponsorships negotiable. Sliding scale pricing available for non-profits & individuals.
Followers view articles on their "dashboard"; this does not contribute to the pageview count unless they click through to view the article on the blog. Metrics for Tumblr views are not available.
Pageview count does not include article views via Tumblr "dashboard".
